19
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,280
Prosím...

20
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:06,180
Prestaň už, dobre?

21
00:01:13,990 --> 00:01:15,560
Videla si Hyun Moo-a?

22
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:17,560
Ublížil ti?

23
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:19,160
Nie, ani sa ma nedotkol.

24
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:22,530
Kde išiel?

25
