49
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,420
Je ti to na smiech?

50
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:06,090
Hyun Moo...

51
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:09,300
Chcel, aby si ho mal rád.

52
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:12,870
