72
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:28,540
Bola to milá ženská.

73
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,850
Vedela ma dobre navigovať.

74
00:05:32,710 --> 00:05:33,710
Lenže...

75
00:05:36,250 --> 00:05:37,820
Lenže ma neposlúchla.

76
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:43,320
Keby si neutiekla a zavolala políciu,

77
00:05:45,930 --> 00:05:48,230
